# Shell Script 
This repository contains my daily practice, exercises, and notes while learning Shell scripting (Bash) on Linux.

# Topics Covered
     Variable declarations and arithmetic operations  
     Conditional statements (`if`, `else`, `elif`, `case`)  
     Loop structures (`for`, `while`, `until`)  
     Functions and argument parsing  
     File handling (searching, filtering, permission checks)  
     Real-world exercises (log analysis, CSV parsing) 
